                {
                  "heading": "NANOSTRAIT",
                  "description": "A next-generation, formaldehyde-free straightening treatment powered by thermal sealing technology to rebuild, realign, and reconstruct the hair fiber from within. It delivers maximum straightness, luxury frizz control, enhanced strength and elasticity, and sleek, luminous hair with long-lasting results.",
